An '''Ibarsi knife''' was a long blade favored by the [[Rabaanite]]s. Almost as long as a [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]], it was used primarily in close combat, but could also be thrown to lethal effect.

[[Mika Streev]] was known to use an Ibarsi knife, and severed [[Modigal Glave]]'s arm using it during an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] ambush on the [[Combat Moon]].<ref name="AJ9">{{JournalCite|9|Combat Moon (short story)}}</ref>

